@startuml diag-001-smoke
' DIAG-001 smoke test -- confirms PlantUML server on port 8010 is reachable
' and the VS Code jebbs.plantuml extension can render via PlantUMLServer mode.
' Preview: Alt+D in VS Code with this file open.

title DIAG-001 Smoke Test\nPlantUML render via Docker (port 8010)

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Courier
skinparam roundcorner 8

actor Developer as dev
node "VS Code\njebbs.plantuml" as vsc
node "Docker\nplantuml-server:jetty\nport 8010" as srv
database "SVG/PNG\noutput" as out

dev --> vsc : Alt+D (preview)
vsc --> srv : HTTP POST /form\n(encoded .puml source)
srv --> vsc : SVG response
vsc --> out : renders in\npreview panel

note right of srv
  plantuml.server = http://localhost:8010
  plantuml.render = PlantUMLServer
end note

note bottom
  PASS criteria: diagram renders without timeout.
  If blank: confirm Docker container is running.
  docker start plantuml-server
end note

@enduml
